Dark Shine Temple Original Tracks

Track 1/9 will be a collection of 9 Progressive Rock/Metal tracks. Track by track will be released every month.

Don't miss them out!  This track includes:

* All tracks in high quality (WAV).

* 1 Master Track 1

* 6 Stems/Multitrack (Drums, Bass, Rhythm Guitars, Synths, Clean Guitars and Lead Guitars)

* Total ownership of this items.

 

If you require more about this track, you can write to darkshinetemple@gmail.com.

 

Dave, 

Audio Engineer 

CEO at Dark Shine Temple Records
